name: The Gift: Iterations of The Great Giver or Tarmarind and the Flower Girl
description:
So much involved in my work and where it comes from, all at once: bold and luminous, painterly, gritty, grotesque, hysterical, historic Histrionic, neo-primitive Byzantine over pot-pourri montage, collage onslaught Treated to various ends for color, (as a palette) as form, as reference, reverence and Design-all treated with this over-calligraphy in my own religious vernacular- a feverish Automatic painting vocabulary, (with infinite, mutating dialects).
